  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "If your repo urls are long, `helm repo list` truncates them. For example, something like:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ helm repo list\r\nNAME     \tURL                                               \r\nstable   \thttp://storage.googleapis.com/kubernetes-charts\r\nincubator\thttps://kubernetes-charts-incubator.storage.goo...\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt would be nice to have either a --verbose flag to `helm repo list`, or `helm repo show [NAME]` to show the full url.",
